comments: Comment on anything. Comments are private.

en-GB.app_desc: Enable credit card payments for your customers. It is an easy, fast, secure and what's the most important - a cheap way of receiving payments. It is very much like the Paypal payments, just without the extortionate fees Paypal charges for large sales. The app integrates with Tradeshift invoices creating a button which takes users to an online payments website of your payment service provider. You will receive a notification when the invoice is payed. By activating this app you subscribe for the early version of the app which is comming soon.
en-GB.form_title: Subscribe for the Credit Card Payments app!
en-GB.give_us_feedback: The Credit Card Payments app is almost ready and will be released soon. Subscribe to be the first to try the early version of the app and get advantage of credit card payments. While you are here, why not giving us some input about the way you receive payments? By doing this you will help us to ensure the app suites your needs and makes a good experience for you.
en-GB.q1_pg: What merchant account provider or payment gateway/service provider do you prefer (for example: Authorize.net, Sagepay, DIBS, etc.):
en-GB.q2_pg_int: Is your merchant account integrated with your bank account so you can automatically receive all your credit card payments directly into your bank account?
en-GB.q3_feedback: And finally, tell us if you have any wishes, concerns or ideas:
